snippet: With a wild finish capping an otherwise dull game filled with turnovers, punts and penalties, Dallas beat Washington on Dan Bailey’s kick with nine seconds to play.
abstract: NFL Roundup; Dallas Cowboys defeat Washington Redskins, 19-16; other football news noted.
lead_paragraph: With a wild finish capping an otherwise dull game filled with turnovers, punts and penalties, Dallas beat Washington on Dan Bailey’s kick with nine seconds to play.
